  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK557">
<l>tuḷiyiṉmai ñālattiṟ keṟṟaṟṟē vēnta </l>
<l>ṉaḷiyiṉmai vāḻu muyirkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As is the world without rain, so live a people whose king is without kindness.</l>
            </lg>
